  "description": "A wide shot of the Golden Gate Bridge under a heavily overcast sky. The bridge, painted a vibrant reddish-orange, spans a body of water, likely the San Francisco Bay. The water is choppy with whitecaps, indicating some wind.  In the foreground, a rocky coastline with dark green vegetation frames the view.  Hills and landmasses are visible in the background, shrouded in mist and clouds. The overall scene is dominated by the gray of the sky and water, contrasting with the bright color of the bridge. The light is diffused and soft, contributing to a somewhat somber atmosphere.",
